<div class="title">Skepticism Replaced by Euphoria</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=RoBsTa&Exact=1">RoBsTa</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; RoBsTa. "Skepticism Replaced by Euphoria: An Experience with AMT (exp22065)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 23, 2008. erowid.org/exp/22065</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
